PrecisAuthority to enter into an AGREEMENT with the Province of NEW BRUNSWICK which provides for the transfer of responsibility for the operation of the ferry terminals at NORTH HEAD and at WALLACE COVE, together with title to the real property and facilities used in connection therewith, and for the making of a financial contribution towards their improvement.
